# ── Runtime state files — VPS-local only, NEVER commit ───────────────
# These are written by the live bot on the VPS every scan/trade.
# Committing them causes git pull to overwrite live VPS state with
# stale repo data → shows fake/broken data on the dashboard.
logs/paper_trades_stocks_only.json
logs/paper_trades.json
logs/latest_signals.json
logs/sectors.json
logs/earnings.json
logs/scan_info.json
